{"tid":435523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應跑手資料被盜　楊偉雄：過多網上登記或添風險","createTime":"2017-10-14T10:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T11:12:58.000Z","uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1420a36c7c42a019e20b4aeeba6bde4512c96699","tid":435523,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:56:57.000Z","msg":"多名跑手在網上以信用卡繳付渣打香港馬拉松報名費後，懷疑被人盜用資料交易，已報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長楊偉雄出席本台節目後表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">網上保安是比較複雜的問題</span>，因為如在網上登記提供太多資料時，會牽涉盜用風險，因為現時互聯網盜用資料，可能是源於用家的手機或電腦。但他認為，香港在保安防禦方面工作做得很好。<br />\n<br />\n楊偉雄說，政府在數碼個人身分投入後，希望在兩年內令市民更安全享用不同電子政府服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1359042-20171014.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1359042-20171014.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qhykyEhMnRht1cruuPfc5aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=38f2802e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1359042-20171014.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3cbf2331\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1359042-20171014.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e6d7b692143f5a855dd9ad21ebd5104e978ccb","tid":435523,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:57:59.000Z","msg":"電子支付呢?"},{"pid":"c720a69efa07033f71d6c0abcb39b3c5d86f334a","tid":435523,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8484a5342ce6ec2bd36e8377d4647c641dd9bb20","tid":435523,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"創科局唔係要克服資訊安全難題咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":